    	<h3>陕西省中医医院北楼部署无线网络设备采购项目招标公告</h3>
      <i>发布时间：2026-07-03 07:55   来源：   浏览次数：<script type='text/javascript' src='/web/news_checknum.rt?contentId=16100&channlId=15'></script></i>
       
        <div style="color:#000000;">
      		<p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:31px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">项目名称：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">陕西省中医医院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">北楼部署无线网络设备</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购项目</span></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购方式：公开招标</span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">项目预算</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">及采购内容：</span></p><table width="525"><tbody><tr style="height:29px" class="firstRow"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">品目名称</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">采购内容</span></p></td><td width="68" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">数量</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">采购预算</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">（</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">元</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:19px">）</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:30px"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">存储用光纤交换机</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">POE交换机及光模块</span></p></td><td width="68" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">8</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">（台）</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">44,952.00</span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:30px"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">路由器</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px"><sp