id solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">23<span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">241.60</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:30px"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">光纤转换器</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">万兆单模光模块</span></p></td><td width="68" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">32</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">（个）</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">18<span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">240.00</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:30px"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">其他信息安全设备</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">单模光纤跳线</span></p></td><td width="68" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">32</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">（根）</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">984.00</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:30px"><td width="146" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">其他信息安全设备</span></p></td><td width="192" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">尾跳线纤、水晶头及其他费用</span></p></td><td width="68" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">1</span><span style="font-family:仿宋;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">（批）</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-align:center;line-height:130%"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">94<span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">256.16</span></span></p></td></tr><tr style="height:35px"><td width="406" valign="center" colspan="3" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:25px"><span style="font-family:宋体;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">合计</span></p></td><td width="119" valign="center" style="padding: 0px 7px; border-width: medium 1px 1px; border-style: none solid solid; border-color: currentcolor windowtext windowtext;"><p style=";text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:25px"><span style="font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;;line-height:130%;font-size:16px">267<span style="font-family:宋体">，</span><span style="font-family:Times New Roman">937.96</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><br/></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">采购需求：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">实现北楼的内外网无线网络全范围覆盖，确保</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">传输速率能满足院内业务系统使用，符合</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">医疗行业网络安全规范</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">实现我院无线终端统一管控。</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　一、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">信息</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名时间：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">202</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">6</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">7月3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">日至</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">20</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">26</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">日</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">每日上午</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">8:30至11:00，下午14:30至17:00，节假日除外</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">）</span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名地点：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">西华门</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">4号莲湖区图书馆陕西省中医医院行政楼</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">公告期限：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2026年7月9日</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">二、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">投标及开标信息</span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标截止时间：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2026年7月22日上午9点整（北京时间）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">开标时间：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">2026年7月22日上午9点整（北京时间）</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:80px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">开标地点：西华门</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">4号莲湖区图书馆陕西省中医医院行政楼</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">三、</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">报名要求：</span></p><p style="margin-left:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">供应商需提供以下资格审查必备文件：</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">1、</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">营业执照或身份证明</span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">供应商合法注册的法人或其他组织的营业执照等证明文件</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">加盖公章</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">，自然人的身份证明；</span> </span></p><p style=";text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">2</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">、</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">授权委托书</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">供应商参加本项目的合法授权人授权委托书；</span> </span></p><p style=";margin-left: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">3、无违法记录声明</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标人应出具参加本次政府采购活动前</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">3年内在经营活动中无重大违法记录,以及未被列入失信被执行人、重大税收违法案件当事人名单、政府采购严重违法失信行为记录的书面声明</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">；</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">4、</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">财务状况</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">证明</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">2024年度以来（任意1年）审计报告或</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">近</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">3个月内出具的银行资信证明</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">；</span></p><p style=";text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">5、</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">税收</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">及</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">社会保障</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">缴纳证明</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">投标截止前</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">6个月内</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px"><span style="font-family:仿宋">任意</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">1个月缴纳税</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">收</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">和社会保障金的缴费凭据（加盖单位公章）；依法不需要缴纳的供应商</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">需提供相关证明文件</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">；</span></p><p style="text-indent:40px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">6、特定资格：</span></strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">供应商需提供电子与智能化工程专业承包一级资质。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;line-height: 29px">　　<span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">以上为资格审查必备资质。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">评标</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">时，根据供应商提供的上述资格证明文件进行资格审查，未通过资格审查的，其响应文件将按无效响应处理</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">。（资格证明文件原件</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">备查</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">）。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;line-height: 29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　本项目不接受联合体。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;line-height: 29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　四、凡对本项目提出询问，请按以下方式联系。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;line-height: 29px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">　　　 &nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">项目联系人：白老师　联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋">029-87252581</span></span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 40px;line-height: 29px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋;font-size: 20px">注：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">前来报名者请提前打电话联系。</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 440px;line-height: 25px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 440px;line-height: 25px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 440px;line-height: 25px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 440px;line-height: 25px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0;text-indent: 440px;line-height: 25px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-right: 0px; text-indent: 440px; line-height: 25px; text-align: right;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">综合运营办公室</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 21px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 21px;"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:20px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋">2026年7月3日</span></span></p><p><br/></p>
      	</div>
    </div>


</div>


